{"tid":1605763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[切記三大要點]前線緊記勿鳩叫亂跑、勿對峙、有人數優勢時主動進攻","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:10:46.000Z","uid":2883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40866c307a23c9ec83922a7235b91f339021bed9","tid":1605763,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"第一，當有狗黎到時唔好鳩叫同亂跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為會影響軍心亦會制造恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後又潰逃，所以驚就真係唔好企咁前<br />\n<br />\n第二，對峙真係大忌黎，又唔攻又唔退死守一個位，比時間班狗部署，之後又變100米跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，有人數優勢時應主動進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時啲狗啱啱黎到會得20至40人，若我方人數有絕對優勢應快速進攻<br />\n<br />\n進攻時應推進速度不可過慢，因為要儘快縮短距離，同時可以一齊大嗌，提升我方士氣又可擾亂敵方心神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而最前排嘅手足一定要有盾有傘，用黎擋布袋彈同橡膠子彈，緊隨其後嘅人要瘋狂遠攻，當去到20米範圍就要全速衝鋒打近戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以尋日灣仔行人天橋為例，喺橋上嘅狗得10隻左右，而我方啲人係一定係超過十倍以上，但係遲遲都唔攻，比班狗係咁射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後有手足喺其中一條樓梯上，但係推得太慢，如果可以分兩邊樓梯一齊快推夾擊，咁班狗實仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb00a468990a808632cb985feeb927821ef71ca2","tid":1605763,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bbef329cc41cdd14d5c391212db18e65ee64102","tid":1605763,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日出去前睇左先<br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvk8a1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnvk8a1d.jpg&h=904ebae9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nvLXGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3nvLXGe.jpg&h=e902aac8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8195e51e0c1df18d152c1a2c96f8dc94700d983b","tid":1605763,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88a43bcc67c74f1e902f2cc173ef9f7226ff9c08","tid":1605763,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}